To grab a frame from the video:

ffmpeg -ss <seconds> -i <input.mp4> -vframes 1 -f image2 <output.jpg>

To get the time, in seconds, for a file

ffprobe -i <input.mp4> -show_entries format=duration -v quiet -of csv="p=0"


